latestPosts.caption:
✨Alexandria Stylebook✨

Closing out the year with a feature in @alxstylebook December Edition! Thank you to @rainbowknycdc for this beautifully crafted piece that paints me as a superwoman, a portrayal I humbly appreciate, though am very far from! ❤️and a major thanks to @reneecgagephoto for these fab photos!! It wasn’t my best hair day, but she somehow made it look like it was 😍📸🔗Link in bio for full article🔗

So grateful for all the opportunities that came out of this year and all the community love and support I’ve received! It’s what keeps me going 🫶🏽Sharing some of my local faves that were mentioned in this article!:

Outfit, matching print set: @lucumaboutique 🫶🏽
Shoot location: @adasontheriver 
Fave spots in Alexandria: @baliansprings , @shesuniquejewelry , @mias_italian_kitchen , @volasdockside 

I have manyyy favorites though and am happy to share them all if you ever need any Alexandria recs!! 🫶🏽 🔗Full link to article in bio🔗

Hope everyone has a great last week of 2023!🥂

latestPosts.caption:
✨GRATEFUL✨ The Intersection between Fashion + Personal Growth. 

I am so incredibly honored to have not only been selected to be on the cover of the @vipalxmag Magazine this month but to be able to chat about the intersection between fashion and personal growth - a subject I am so passionate about it. 💃🏽 As you read more of my take on the two in this story, you’ll learn more about me me as a whole. Would love to hear your thoughts 😊 VIP covers so many amazing stories on local creators and businesses, and is highly recommend subscribing to stay up to date with it all! 

Thanks to @by_kellie and @vipalxmag for this amazing feature that was so well written by @liesel.schmidt And thank you to all of YOU who continuously support my BasicBalance journey! I’m so grateful for opportunities like this and for such a supportive community. Love you all ❤️

You can browse through the entire magazine and read my story here: https://issuu.com/vipalxmag/docs/vip-vol6-issue2

All of my photos featured in this cover are by the @timelinedcphoto 📸

latestPosts.caption:
FIVE years of BasicBalance🥳🥂

And just like that… five years have flown by & I am nothing but grateful for all the opportunities that have come my way  and most importantly, so grateful for all of you + your endless love and support over the years, especially those that have been around since day one! ✨

I had no idea what I was getting into when I started BB - I just knew I wanted a creative space that was a breathe of fresh air from my heavy 9-5 work, where I can share the things I love that bring me joy. And here we are…. many opportunities & newfound friendships later! Thank you for being here and thank you for making it easy to share bits and pieces of my day to day life with you. Love you ALL. To many more🥂💕 #wemadeit 

PS: Huge shoutout to @cakesbylalae for this fabulous cake that was so hard to eat bc it was too pretty to cut! And thank you to @timelinedcphoto for capturing this milestone so beautifully! @daniellajaramillomua did my make up for this shoot and nailed the natural look I was looking for! Three people who have always supported my visions without a doubt! 🫶🏽

xoxo, 
BB💋

latestPosts.caption:
Suns out, smiles out 🙃

Hi, friends! Who else is loving this weather?! It’s hot but it’s SUMMER and I am so excited for summer fashion again! I feel like I have been popping in and out of here. This year has just been so busy for me and while I don’t exactly feel like I’m super behind on my BB venture, I also do at the same time - so forgive me for not keeping up with activity as often as I used to!! Different seasons of life come with different sets of demands and that’s where I’m at right now! 🫶🏽

HOWEVER, I love you all, and I am loving seeing all the life updates from my fellow creators and even some of you who I’ve also been following in turn for years! So keep them coming. :) 

Hope you’re having a good week!! I promise to link ALL my recent looks over the next two weeks!! 🔗

————

latestPosts.caption:
When your vision is effortlessly brought to life✨

Are you looking for a studio to capture milestone memories?! Still not over this fabulous shoot at @dmvluxstudios with my favorite @kathleenmariephoto for my birthday shoot last month! 📸

You know I love birthdays and capturing alll the memories! Getting equally as loud over the small wins vs. the big wins is how I roll! @dmvluxstudios has multiple spacious rooms to shoot in with natural light shining iin - which is a must! Had no idea this studio existed until recently - this gem is tucked away in the heart of Fairfax📍

📸Use code NANCY10 for 10% off your first booking📸

Sunshine on a cloudy day☀️

Hi, friends!! Happy Wednesday! It’s been a minute since I’ve posted because I’ve just been frocking all over the place this month. So many back to back traveling and events! Just wrapped up a super fun and fabulous wedding weekend celebrating testing a good friend! Having major withdrawals! If you caught my stories, then you know we had a good time!! 💃🏽

How is everyone doing?! This rain is not IT. Where did this come from!? Isn’t summer is around the corner, Mother Nature needs to stop it with this rubbish 😂 Hope you all are having a great week!🫶🏽

latestPosts.caption:
Happy Friday!! ☀️

Almost had an unintentional Marilyn Monroe moment with this shoot - the wind is always out to get me🤭 How’s everyone doing?! The sun is shining in the DMV after a few days of rain, so much fog, and lots of humidity. Summer is on its way and so are my heat complaints 😂

I’ve got an extremely busy May but much to look forward to! If you know of a way to slow down time, please let me know lol. How’s the rest of your month looking? Bright and productive, hopefully!! Have a fab weekend, friends!!

latestPosts.caption:
Chic, elevated, and always on point🎀

Switched hair salons last year which is never an easy decision to make, but I am so glad I did! Started going to @ombresalonandspa over a year ago and I can finally vouche for the excellence, care, and delivery this salon has to offer! 

Staffed with professionals, @marwa_j_alsaadi has done wonders for my hair! I have naturally dark hair and it took forever and a lot of patience to bring me to the light ashy blonde I love! Was told many times I can’t get there without damaging my hair, but Marwa has found a work around to maintain the health of my hair while meeting my expectations! 

Side note: This salon looks like it’s straight out of a Pinterest board!? So chic,  and my IG content girlies would have a field day in here! 

If you’re looking for a new salon or stylist, @ombresalonandspa is IT - I get compliments on my color often and it’s all thanks to Marwa!💕

latestPosts.caption:
POV: You celebrate your birthday at one of DC’s newest + hottest brunch spots in the city 💃🏽

Had the best time kicking off another year of life with my people at @barangie.dc last weekend! ❤️Still feeling alll the love! @barangie.dc just rolled out their brunch menu and I want to say we were probably some of the firsts to try it and everyone was so happy with the food and drinks! 

But wait until you head over for a night on the town — you have to try their dirty martinis! 🍸 Completely different vibe at night! Book your next event or dinner restaurant at @barangie.dc - I promise you’ll love it 🫶🏽

Thank you all for the birthday wishes - I am truly so grateful ❤️

DND: Celebrating 37 trips around the sun today 🎉🎂

Blessed. Grateful. Happy. So grateful to be able to celebrate another year of life! Life is wild, but it runs a little smoother when you’re surrounded by incredible family, solid friendships, and good people! ❤️ I’ve learned that while things may not always go as planned, everything always ends up working out for the better and in my favor - and I am always grateful for that! Lots of pivots along the way, but living my best life and I wouldn’t want any other way! 

Cheers another year of growth, success, lots of laughter, and good times!! 🥂🎉
